description: The GraphCode represents the scene where Maria is swimming in a pool. 'Maria' is identified as the subject (type 1 - object), 'swim' is the activity (type 4 - activity), and 'pool' is the object (type 1 - object). The relation between 'Maria' and 'swim' is defined by the 'perform' relation (type 8 - perform). The other diagonal entries are filled with identity mappings (type 1).
